    "page_title": "",
    "page_admin_only": "false",
    "site_name": "蚕豆私服",
    "site_urls": "https://30hb.cn"
  },
  {
    "id": "36",
    "rid": "35",
    "content": "道歉就免了，但愿下次发病时能把本站给忘了，\n懒得接 AI 审核，词库和在线服务够用，\n反正一年到头也遇不见几次这类人…",
    "ua": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 11.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36",
